data.description: Experience the allure of this delightful brick ranch situated in Lakewood. Enjoy the proximity to a nearby park for recreational activities, and take leisurely strolls through the wooded areas or the serene streets of the neighborhood. The third bedroom, currently utilized as an office, offers versatility, serving as either a third bedroom or a dining area. There are two large living spaces: a den and a living room featuring a wood-burning fireplace. There are new kitchen appliances, all replaced within the last year, and hardwood floors are hidden beneath the carpet in the bedrooms. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this beautiful home. Some photos have been virtually staged using Artificial Intelligence
